Class CSVFileHandler

java.lang.Object
util.CSVFileHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileDataHandler
public class CSVFileHandler extends Object implements FileDataHandler
The CSVFileHandler class provides utility methods for reading and writing user and project data to and from CSV files. It implements the FileDataHandler interface and handles persistence for Applicants, Officers, Managers, and Projects.
